snippet.title: Selaco - Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Selaco was a miracle for the refugees of Earth. A beacon of hope in their darkest hour. Dawn lost everything when Earth fell and dedicated her life to protecting her new home. Hope burned bright, but something lurked in the shadows.

EARLY ACCESS LAUNCH DATE:
May 2024

The Early Access contains:
- 25 open levels (excluding Secret Level)
- 11 fully upgradable weapons
- Full open-source modding support

Wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592280/Selaco/

You can get a Dawn Plush here. As a bonus, you will receive a password to an extra demo level!

https://www.makeship.com/products/dawn-plush
